- Review device placement periodically
- Warranty of Argox AI-6801 Wireless Barcode Reader What is covered? The warranty covers main parts for 1 year (except accidental damage).
- How to factory reset Argox AI-6801 wireless barcode reader. Press and hold the Reset button for about 10 seconds until the status light flashes.

## Troubleshooting

### Won''t turn on / No Power

**Symptoms:** Status light does not light. The machine doesn''t work.

**Resolution:**
1. Check the power cord and plug.
2. Check the adapter to see if it works properly.
3. Contact the service center if internal parts are damaged.

Contact support if issues persist.

## Training

- **Basic course on how to use the Argox AI-6801 wireless barcode reader** (Beginner) — Learn how to install and use the Argox AI-6801 wireless barcode reader. since the beginning Complete with tips for correct settings

## Summary

The Argox AI-6801 wireless barcode reader is a professional professional equipment and technology solutions solution from Professional for commercial and enterprise environments.

**Key Highlights:**
- Professional-grade construction
- Integration with Professional management ecosystem
- Comprehensive documentation and support
- Suitable for commercial and enterprise infrastructure deployment applications')
