- Warranty of ZKTeco UA400 Fingerprint Scanner Record working time What is covered? The warranty covers main parts for 1 year (except accidental damage).
- How to factory reset ZKTeco UA400 Fingerprint Scanner Record working time. Press and hold the Reset button for about 10 seconds until the status light flashes.

## Troubleshooting

### Won''t turn on / No Power

**Symptoms:** Status light does not light. The machine doesn''t work.

**Resolution:**
1. Check the power cord and plug.
2. Check the adapter to see if it works properly.
3. Contact the service center if internal parts are damaged.

Contact support if issues persist.

## Training

- **Course for using ZKTeco UA400 fingerprint scanner Basic working time recording** (Beginner) — Learn how to install and use the ZKTeco UA400 fingerprint scanner. Record working time since the beginning Complete with tips for correct settings

## Summary

The ZKTeco UA400 Fingerprint Scanner Work time recorder is a professional physical access control and entry management solution from ZKTeco for commercial and enterprise environments.

**Key Highlights:**
- Professional-grade construction
- Integration with ZKTeco management ecosystem
