- Set up automatic firmware update notifications
- Regularly verify camera alignment and clean lens
- Implement network segmentation for surveillance traffic
- Warranty of HIKVISION NVR 16CH HVS-7616NXI-K2/16P What is covered? The warranty covers main parts for 1 year (except accidental damage).
- How to reset factory settings for HIKVISION NVR 16CH HVS-7616NXI-K2/16P. Press and hold the Reset button for about 10 seconds until the status light flashes.

## Troubleshooting

### Won''t turn on / No Power

**Symptoms:** Status light does not light. The machine doesn''t work.

**Resolution:**
1. Check the power cord and plug.
2. Check the adapter to see if it works properly.
3. Contact the service center if internal parts are damaged.

Contact support if issues persist.

## Training

- **Basic course for using HIKVISION NVR 16CH HVS-7616NXI-K2/16P** (Beginner) — Learn how to install and use HIKVISION NVR 16CH HVS-7616NXI-K2/16P. since the beginning Complete with tips for correct settings

