4. Connect to network and configure settings
5. Test all functions before finalizing installation
6. Document IP configuration and physical location
7. After installation, verify operation. Check the power cord and plug.

Refer to the Hikvision DS-K1T343EWX User Manual for detailed procedures.

## Best Practices

