- Monitor client density and throughput metrics
- Keep firmware current for performance and security
- Document network topology and mounting locations
- What does the warranty for Hikvision POE Switch(DS-3E0326P-E) 24 Port Fast Ethernet Unmanaged cover? The warranty covers main parts for 1 year (except accidental damage).
- How to reset factory settings for Hikvision POE Switch(DS-3E0326P-E) 24 Port Fast Ethernet Unmanaged. Press and hold the Reset button for about 10 seconds until the status light blinks.

## Troubleshooting

### Won''t turn on / No Power

**Symptoms:** Status light does not light. The machine doesn''t work.

**Resolution:**
1. Check the power cord and plug.
2. Check the adapter to see if it works properly.
3. Contact the service center if internal parts are damaged.

Contact support if issues persist.

## Training

- **Basic course for using Hikvision POE Switch(DS-3E0326P-E) 24 Port Fast Ethernet Unmanaged** (Beginner) — Learn how to install and use Hikvision POE Switch(DS-3E0326P-E) 24 Port Fast Ethernet Unmanaged from scratch. Complete with tips for correct settings

## Summary

